{"tid":1091013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：美國要求中國 2025 年前履行採購承諾","createTime":"2019-04-04T00:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T01:07:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a9d4408af193d9dce89b2cf1b3a2373a61123ff","tid":1091013,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:48:07.000Z","msg":"《彭博社》週三 (3 日) 報導，美國和中國的貿易協議將使中國在 2025 年前履行商品採購承諾，並允許美國公司在中國境內開設全資企業。<br />\n<br />\n美中貿易談判 3 日 於華府重啟新一輪談判，中國副總理劉鶴已經抵達美國華盛頓，雙方進行第 9 輪貿易談判。<br />\n<br />\n兩國目前的目標是針對核心問題達成協議，以便促成美國總統川普和中國領導人習近平的簽約峰會。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博社》引述多位消息人士表示，根據正在擬定的美中貿易協議，中國將在 2025 年前購買更多的美國商品，包括美國黃豆、能源產品，還必須允許在中國經營的美國公司 100％ 的外國所有權，這些是具有約束力的承諾，若中國無法實現承諾，將引發美國後續報復。<br />\n<br />\n週二 (2 日) 美國商會副總裁 Myron Brilliant 表示，美國美中貿易談判正處於最後階段，書面協議的 90% 已完成，但剩餘的 10% 是最困難的部分，也是最棘手的部分，需要雙方進行權衡。<br />\n<br />\n白宮經濟顧問庫德洛表示，美國和中國之間的談判取得良好的進展，雙方都希望本週接近達成協議，但警告最終協議仍然是難以捉摸。<br />\n<br />\n庫德洛稱：「懸而未決的主要問題，包括保護美國智慧財產權與執行機制，用來確保中國履行貿易協議中的承諾。」<br />\n<br />\n美國和中國貿易代表仍在討論雙方領袖何時簽署貿易協議，據了解最早可能在本週四 (4 日) 宣布。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.cnyes.com/news/id/4298240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.cnyes.com%2Fnews%2Fid%2F4298240&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=86af0a67\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.cnyes.com/news/id/4298240</a><br />\n<br />\n2025<br />\n侵侵第二任期都完咗（連任既話）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a34f5666ebd048db0579ce376ee8d666d43653","tid":1091013,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T00:55:16.000Z","msg":"2025 笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起香港普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a93952407c461f02e15d4eca083c858cf453e7","tid":1091013,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"戇尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"544d843a2b21640270ff17ad1b89c90241d3c1bd","tid":1091013,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:02:55.000Z","msg":"到2025會話份約已成歷史文件<br />\n又赢"},{"pid":"abc32ab578db95141b97b1c5806ee03215cebe28","tid":1091013,"uid":49071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd4bd13a321324d9453b3e28c059d2b22a6592c","tid":1091013,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:04:09.000Z","msg":"係就一早簽咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺明仲有啲致命內容冇講啦"},{"pid":"ba4fedcf281b6a533b642dd871f11a450c7a44bb","tid":1091013,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T01:05:26.000Z","msg":"曬鳩氣<br />\n今時今日仲信個人為製造出嚟既人口屎場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266a69e328bef3fd28db77b2d72b60868ebe2ea0","tid":1091013,"uid":36134,"l